Package fr.cnrs.iees.properties.impl

Class CompoundPropertyListImpl

java.lang.Object
fr.cnrs.iees.properties.impl.CompoundPropertyListImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
PropertyListGetters, PropertyListSetters, ReadOnlyPropertyList, SimplePropertyList, fr.ens.biologie.generic.DataContainer, fr.ens.biologie.generic.Sizeable, Cloneable
public class CompoundPropertyListImpl extends Object implements SimplePropertyList

A property list made by grouping property lists in a single wrapper. Storage is made in the original property lists.

Since property lists may have properties with the same names, the names must be prefixed with a property list name when accessing the properties

Author:
gignoux - 15 juin 2017
